en.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/T%C3%A2n-di-%E1%BB%95/poem-rtRo3olIWOYF0ukEtbT7mQ">Tân di ổ - 辛夷塢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/author-28bVUu4eMEqyWDansRayiw">Bùi Địch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-S%C3%A1i-Hy-L%E1%BB%97-%C4%91%C3%B4-u%C3%BD-ho%C3%A0n-L%C5%A9ng-H%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n-k%C3%BD-Cao-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-th%C6%B0-k%C3%BD/poem-84pNUNntDSUCkeWSBLVMWw">Tống Sái Hy Lỗ đô uý hoàn Lũng Hữu, nhân ký Cao tam thập ngũ thư ký - 送蔡希魯都尉還隴右因寄高三十五書記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Hoa/Xu%C3%A2n-du-ng%C3%A2m/poem-f-14hV_90-FITQyJMfeSHw">Xuân du ngâm - 春遊吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Hoa/author-QPqtGH0DoOgqe6s84Y3CFw">Lý Hoa</a>)<br></div>	</div>
